{"article_id":"PWnZ5FCqycqQnw1h","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"JERUSALEM , Israel -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"More than 60 influential U.S. Christian leaders sent a letter to President Donald Trump","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"urging him to recognize Jerusalem as Israel 's capital","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and move the U.S. Embassy there .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"But a White House official told Reuters","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"though President Trump wants to move the embassy to Jerusalem ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"he wo n't do it now","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"since he feels","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"it would complicate a resumption of Israeli-Palestinian negotiations .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"It was a campaign promise","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"candidate Donald Trump stated over and over .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"`` We will move the American embassy to the eternal capital of the Jewish people , Jerusalem , ''","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"he frequently said on the campaign trail , inevitably to resounding applause .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"when President Trump visits Israel ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"he wo n't fulfill that promise .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"It 's yet another chapter in American 's long diplomatic history in the Holy Land .","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"The first U.S. consulate ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"established in 1844 ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"stood inside the walls of the Old City , near the Jaffa Gate .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Now the building is used by the Christian Information Center .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"In 1912 , the consulate moved just a few blocks away to a place","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"called Prophet 's Street .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Then it moved to a location","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"where the U.S. representative to the Palestinian Authority now sits .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"This consulate reports directly to the State Department","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"rather than the U.S. Embassy in Tel Aviv .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"About a 10-minute drive away stands a U.S. government building","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that provides consular services for U.S. citizens .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"All of this","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"while the embassy sits in Tel Aviv .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"After the White House announcement","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"not to move the embassy now ,","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"the question remains , will it ever make it up to Jerusalem ?","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"More than 20 years ago , David Parsons , media director of the International Christian Embassy Jerusalem","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"( ICEJ ) ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"helped draft the 1995 Jerusalem Embassy Act .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"`` We actually met with [ Arizona ] Senator John Kyl up on Capitol Hill one day","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"and we gauged","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that he was serious ...","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"that moving the embassy was an issue","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"that he wanted to do on principle .","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"It was n't politics .","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"It was principle","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"and he asked us to draft a bill , ''","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Parsons told News .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"`` But ... as the bill went through the sausage grinder of Congress ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"it changed ...","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"They added this presidential waiver authority ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"which it was intended to gut the bill , ''","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"Parsons explained .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"`` It said","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"every six months , the president can suspend this bill","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"if he certifies","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"it 's in U.S. national security interests .","depth":15},{"id":55,"text":"It 's fear","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"that has kept us out . ''","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"For more than two decades , successive presidents have signed that waiver .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"The current one expires June 1 .","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"In addition to national security , another reason","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"given","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"for invoking the waiver","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"is that the U.S. is supposed to be an honest broker .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"How would you address the concern","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"- or criticism -","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"that some people have ?","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"If you do this ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"you undermine the `` peace process ''","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"and you 'll be undermining the ability","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"to negotiate a deal .","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"`` I think","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"at least putting our embassy in West Jerusalem would actually strengthen the peace process , ''","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"Parsons said .","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"`` It would give Israel confidence","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"that its ally , America , is behind it .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"And I think","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"that the longer the nations wait to do this ,","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"the bigger and bigger the question of Jerusalem becomes .","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"Parsons says","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Jerusalem seems to be on a 50-year cycle of favor .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"`` But","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"when you look at ,","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"you see ,","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"not only the last 50 years","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"when the city was reunified in 1967 , ''","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"Parsons continued .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"`` In 100 years ago ,","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"when Allenby , the British general , marched into the city ,","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"liberated it from the Ottoman Turks ,","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"just as the British government was committing to building a Jewish state here .","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"Even 150 years ago , 1867 , General Warren discovered the Old City , the original City of David , south of the Temple Mount ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"and each of these things , every 50 years , something happening in Jerusalem","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"to really free it","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"and release it into its prophetic purposes . ''","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Israeli leaders hope","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"that 'one day ' includes relocating the embassy . `` Well you know ,","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"Israel reunited Jerusalem 50 years ago , in 1967 .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"But the connection with the Jewish people to Jerusalem spiritually goes back 2,000 years , ''","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"Dore Gold , president of the Jerusalem Center for Public Affairs","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"( JCPA )","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"told News .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"`` And our claim , our presence in Jerusalem , has been here for decades...","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"Jews have been streaming back to their ancient capital for years .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"And the movement of the embassy from Tel Aviv to Jerusalem is an American recognition of the special ties of Jerusalem to the Jewish people .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"It may be symbolic ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"but it goes to the core of the identity of Israel . '' `` I think","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"the U.S. moving the embassy to Jerusalem is the right thing","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"to do .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"It 's -","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"it 's way overdue","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"and , of course , it would be a blessing to - to the U.S , ''","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Parsons said .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"In 1950 , Israel declared Jerusalem as its capital .","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"In 1967 , it captured the Old City and the eastern part of Jerusalem .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Then in 1980 , Israel passed the Basic Law Jerusalem","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"that incorporated all of the land","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"captured in 1967","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"as its capital .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"That 's when most embassies left Jerusalem for Tel Aviv","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"and ICEJ moved in .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"`` To represent Christians from all over the world","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"who want to stand in solidarity with Israel ,","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"help secure it","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"and help it reach its destiny","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"and also want to stand in solidarity with their claim and connection to Jerusalem , ''","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"Parsons said .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"And","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"whether or not the U.S. Embassy eventually moves to Jerusalem ,","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"Parsons sees a glorious future for the city .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"`` This is that promised Son of David , the Messiah ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"[ who ] will rule","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"and reign over the world in peace and righteousness","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"and , of course , we 're Christians , ''","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"Parsons said .","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"`` We believe","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"that 's Jesus ,","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"but I think","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"a house of prayer for all people , that exalted throne of the Messiah during the Messianic age .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"This is Israel 's ultimate destiny and Jerusalem 's . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":277,"left":0,"right":276,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":276,